                "invention-title": [
                    "Adsorbent regeneration system and method in pressure swing adsorption tower",
                    "一种变压吸附塔中的吸附剂再生系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The adsorbent regeneration system comprises a heat exchanger, a cold gas inlet of the heat exchanger is communicated with a first flow meter, a hot gas outlet of the heat exchanger alternately enters a first adsorption tower or a second adsorption tower through a first control pipeline, and adsorbent regeneration is achieved through high-temperature gas; according to the hydrogen power generation device, regeneration of an adsorbent of the pressure swing adsorption tower is achieved through hot hydrogen heated by waste heat of the hydrogen power generator, and meanwhile waste hydrogen obtained after the adsorbent is regenerated is used for combustion to generate power to be supplied to a compressor to compress hydrogen; and hydrogen treatment modularization and system energy gradient utilization are achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种变压吸附塔中的吸附剂再生系统及方法，包括换热器，所述换热器的冷气体入口与第一流量计连通，热气体出口通过第一控制管路交替进入第一吸附塔或第二吸附塔内，通过高温气体实现吸附剂再生；所述换热器的热气体入口与氢发电机尾气出口连通，冷气体出口与尾气检测器连通，本发明使用氢发电机余热加热的热氢气实现变压吸附塔吸附剂再生，同时使用再生吸附剂后的废氢进行燃烧发电供压缩机压缩氢气，实现氢气处理模块化与系统能量梯级利用。"
                }
            ]
